      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PENNY PINCHER (2) broke a string of placings finishing in the money two on end before a last start fourth (23.11) at this track. Form here sound including three wins. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to her name from three starts. Looks the one to beat on her best form. SIX STORY SYD (1) turned in a modest effort most recently when seventh at this track over 300m behind Rosetta Street (17.60) in a Grade 5. Cannot be taken lightly. WEST ON ROSE (8) stalked lead from an outside box last start before finishing second (22.87) at this track in a Grade 6 over 400m. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from six starts. Expected to be in this for a long way. SUNSET VENDETTA (6) cannot be written off despite a miss here at his latest outing.",
